    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Local Open Scope profunctor_scope.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Section identity.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n  (** Quoting nLab:\n\n      In particular the identity profunctor [Id : C \u21f8 C] is represented by the identity functor and hence is given by the hom-functor [C(\u2212,\u2212) : C\u1d52\u1d56 \u00d7 C \u2192 Set]. *)\n\n  "
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Definition identity `{Funext} (C : PreCategory) : C -|-> C\n    := hom_functor C.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "End identity.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Module Export ProfunctorIdentityNotations.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n  "
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Notation \"1\" := (identity _) : profunctor_scope.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "End ProfunctorIdentityNotations.",
      "messages": [],
